name: MYNT'S RESOURCES
body:
### Hello!
This Github page is just a place for me to chuck all my resources for my digital designs and etc. There's nothing to see here, so just move along. Shoo.

### About Me
I'm an Art Director based in Malaysia. I like codings and designing for websites. So you will find most of my javascript, css and html files being hosted here.

### Contact
If you really feel like you need to contact me no matter what, please do send me an email at jaemint[@]yahoo[dot]com.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
